            Set to true if your client can resolve datanode hostnames (e.g., 'datanode' in Docker network).
            Set to false if datanodes report their IP addresses and clients need to connect directly to IPs.
            In most Docker setups, 'true' or omitting this property (which often defaults to true) works.
        </description>
    </property>
